00:06:41.950 --> 00:06:42.950 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Tough question.

00:06:42.950 --> 00:06:43.750 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: I know.

00:06:43.750 --> 00:06:47.360 align:middle line:84%
I tell all my clients, it's
God's will, it's not mine.

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:51.980 align:middle line:84%
I show up clear, I show
up as a very clear vessel

00:06:51.980 --> 00:06:56.180 align:middle line:84%
