energy in and I do the work.

00:06:56.180 --> 00:06:58.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's God's
will, it's not mine.

00:06:58.190 --> 00:07:00.320 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You have an
inner peace about you

00:07:00.320 --> 00:07:01.740 align:middle line:90%
when you're working on people.

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:03.320 align:middle line:90%
How does that work for you?

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:05.480 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: Well, I
teach people how

00:07:05.480 --> 00:07:07.790 align:middle line:90%
to access their inner peace.

00:07:07.790 --> 00:07:10.640 align:middle line:84%
And through 40
years of meditation,

00:07:10.640 --> 00:07:16.910 align:middle line:84%
I've really come to understand
that although I grew up

00:07:16.910 --> 00:07:20.720 align:middle line:84%
at a time when peace
was really important

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:23.090 align:middle line:84%
and give peace a chance
and you and I can think

00:07:23.090 --> 00:07:26.600 align:middle line:84%
of all kinds of songs
about peace, Vietnam War,

00:07:26.600 --> 00:07:30.110 align:middle line:84%
all of the things that brought
about people wanting peace,

00:07:30.110 --> 00:07:33.260 align:middle line:84%
I believe peace really
exists within us.

00:07:33.260 --> 00:07:35.990 align:middle line:90%
It's inside our soul body.

00:07:35.990 --> 00:07:38.300 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: You have a series
called "The Earth Angel

00:07:38.300 --> 00:07:39.380 align:middle line:90%
Diaries."

00:07:39.380 --> 00:07:40.730 align:middle line:90%
Let's look.

00:07:40.730 --> 00:07:43.430 align:middle line:10%
>>GRACE: We don't
understand peace

00:07:43.430 --> 00:07:48.200 align:middle line:10%
if we have not necessarily
experienced disruption

00:07:48.200 --> 00:07:50.510 align:middle line:10%
and not being peaceful.

00:07:50.510 --> 00:07:53.210 align:middle line:10%
A lot of people
come from countries

00:07:53.210 --> 00:07:56.570 align:middle line:10%
that are war torn and
post-traumatic stress

00:07:56.570 --> 00:08:00.440 align:middle line:10%
and everything that
is opposite of peace.

00:08:00.440 --> 00:08:07.740 align:middle line:10%
And we have had for centuries
disruption and war, famine,

00:08:07.740 --> 00:08:11.510 align:middle line:10%
plague, you name
it, it has kept us

00:08:11.510 --> 00:08:18.430 align:middle line:10%
from this desire, this feeling
of wanting to have peace.

00:08:18.430 --> 00:08:22.860 align:middle line:10%
So here we are today,
plague, disruption,

00:08:22.860 --> 00:08:25.770 align:middle line:10%
all kinds of things
going on around the world

00:08:25.770 --> 00:08:28.080 align:middle line:10%
and we are looking for peace.

00:08:28.080 --> 00:08:29.520 align:middle line:10%
So how do we find that?

00:08:29.520 --> 00:08:33.840 align:middle line:10%
How do we get back to
our own inner peace?

00:08:33.840 --> 00:08:37.049 align:middle line:10%
This is inside your soul body.

00:08:37.049 --> 00:08:39.750 align:middle line:10%
Your soul body
inhabits your body.

00:08:39.750 --> 00:08:45.670 align:middle line:10%
At the very center of your
soul body is inner peace.

00:08:45.670 --> 00:08:49.560 align:middle line:10%
So instead of looking outside
of ourselves for peace,

00:08:49.560 --> 00:08:52.950 align:middle line:10%
we need to go within
and we need to connect

00:08:52.950 --> 00:08:56.100 align:middle line:10%
with this inner peace
through meditation.

00:08:56.100 --> 00:08:59.737 align:middle line:10%
What pulls us out of
that feeling of peace,

00:08:59.737 --> 00:09:02.070 align:middle line:10%
you know what it's like when
you walk through the garden

00:09:02.070 --> 00:09:04.200 align:middle line:10%
and you feel so peaceful.

00:09:04.200 --> 00:09:08.430 align:middle line:10%
The birds are singing, there's
hummingbirds coming by,

00:09:08.430 --> 00:09:10.440 align:middle line:10%
it's such a peaceful feeling.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:15.830 align:middle line:10%
What takes us out
of that dysfunction?

00:09:15.830 --> 00:09:20.240 align:middle line:10%
When we aren't focusing
ourselves in a way

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:23.090 align:middle line:10%
that helps us to
stay in that peace,

00:09:23.090 --> 00:09:27.410 align:middle line:10%
but rather we get addicted
to the shock and the fear

00:09:27.410 --> 00:09:29.660 align:middle line:10%
and the betrayal and
all the things that

00:09:29.660 --> 00:09:32.570 align:middle line:10%
were, "oh, my God,
tell me that again.

00:09:32.570 --> 00:09:35.270 align:middle line:10%
Oh, it was way too scary,
but I want to hear it again."

00:09:35.270 --> 00:09:40.010 align:middle line:10%
We're addicted to a part of
the pattern and cycle that

00:09:40.010 --> 00:09:46.880 align:middle line:10%
is not about peace, but rather
disruption and shock and fear.

00:09:46.880 --> 00:09:51.680 align:middle line:10%
So in order to get out of those
feelings, we must ground them.

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:52.760 align:middle line:10%
You've got to feel them.

00:09:52.760 --> 00:09:53.720 align:middle line:10%
You have them.

00:09:53.720 --> 00:09:57.290 align:middle line:10%
Feel them, let them go
deep into the Earth.

00:09:57.290 --> 00:10:03.380 align:middle line:10%
Just ground them into the Earth,
then get back to your peace,

