>>NOORY: When you are
on this kind of journey,

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:25.380 align:middle line:84%
do you recollect it
when you come back?

00:29:25.380 --> 00:29:30.270 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: I do, and oftentimes
it's hours and hours later.

00:29:30.270 --> 00:29:33.060 align:middle line:90%
I feel the cold, I feel rain.

00:29:33.060 --> 00:29:33.930 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: The heat.

00:29:33.930 --> 00:29:37.260 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: I have all
the sensations, yes.

00:29:37.260 --> 00:29:39.390 align:middle line:84%
And I always think
I'm just going

00:29:39.390 --> 00:29:41.790 align:middle line:84%
to be gone for 20 minutes,
and it's like three four

00:29:41.790 --> 00:29:43.337 align:middle line:84%
or five hours
later and I'm back.

00:29:43.337 --> 00:29:44.670 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Earth time, Earth time.

00:29:44.670 --> 00:29:45.000 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: Yeah.

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:46.800 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Have you ever
traveled to a place

00:29:46.800 --> 00:29:48.420 align:middle line:90%
that you didn't want to be in?

00:29:48.420 --> 00:29:48.840 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: Yes.

00:29:48.840 --> 00:29:49.500 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Where.

00:29:49.500 --> 00:29:50.300 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: I did.

00:29:50.300 --> 00:29:53.340 align:middle line:84%
Well, there was one time when
I went to the Great Pyramid

00:29:53.340 --> 00:29:55.402 align:middle line:90%
and Anubis was there.

00:29:55.402 --> 00:29:56.360 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What's Anubis?

00:29:56.360 --> 00:29:58.740 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: Anubis is
the Egyptian God

00:29:58.740 --> 00:30:01.390 align:middle line:84%
that looks like a Dog
with a pointy face.

00:30:01.390 --> 00:30:07.500 align:middle line:84%
He is the God who handled
death and beyond, one of them.

00:30:07.500 --> 00:30:09.960 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: They didn't scare you?

00:30:09.960 --> 00:30:11.370 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: It was scary, yes.

00:30:11.370 --> 00:30:17.340 align:middle line:84%
It was sort of an inquiry of who
were we and why were we there.

00:30:17.340 --> 00:30:19.710 align:middle line:90%
So we got out of there fast.

00:30:19.710 --> 00:30:23.220 align:middle line:84%
There was another time my
spirit traveled to a place

00:30:23.220 --> 00:30:26.820 align:middle line:84%
where it was after
the fall of Lemuria

00:30:26.820 --> 00:30:29.970 align:middle line:84%
and it was off
the coast of where

00:30:29.970 --> 00:30:32.610 align:middle line:90%
Lemuria used to be in Japan.

00:30:32.610 --> 00:30:37.140 align:middle line:84%
And there were these beings
that were alien in nature

00:30:37.140 --> 00:30:38.190 align:middle line:90%
that were there.

00:30:38.190 --> 00:30:40.020 align:middle line:90%
And it was very scary.

00:30:40.020 --> 00:30:44.040 align:middle line:84%
And I looked at my guides
and I said, "OK, we saw it.

00:30:44.040 --> 00:30:45.240 align:middle line:90%
Now we got to go."

00:30:45.240 --> 00:30:47.470 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES] And we left.

00:30:47.470 --> 00:30:50.100 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: So what is your
meditation peace project.

00:30:50.100 --> 00:30:51.900 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: The meditation
peace project

00:30:51.900 --> 00:30:57.930 align:middle line:84%
is a free one hour meditation
that I do once a month on Zoom.

00:30:57.930 --> 00:31:01.020 align:middle line:84%
I have people from all over
the world who come together.

00:31:01.020 --> 00:31:03.660 align:middle line:84%
I talk them through my
grounding meditation.

00:31:03.660 --> 00:31:06.630 align:middle line:84%
We go into a deep
state of inner peace

00:31:06.630 --> 00:31:09.360 align:middle line:84%
and we literally
worked on ourselves

00:31:09.360 --> 00:31:11.370 align:middle line:90%
and we work on the planet.

00:31:11.370 --> 00:31:13.780 align:middle line:84%
We're not sending
energy anywhere,

00:31:13.780 --> 00:31:16.380 align:middle line:84%
we're not manipulating
anything anywhere.

00:31:16.380 --> 00:31:20.250 align:middle line:84%
We're simply holding
that vibration.

00:31:20.250 --> 00:31:23.460 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: One of the great
people for intention experiments

00:31:23.460 --> 00:31:25.650 align:middle line:84%
has been Lynne
McTaggart, and she

00:31:25.650 --> 00:31:29.378 align:middle line:84%
was interviewed by Regina
Meredith about meditation.

00:31:29.378 --> 00:31:31.170 align:middle line:10%
>>LYNNE MCTAGGART: We
have this big problem

00:31:31.170 --> 00:31:33.780 align:middle line:10%
on a giant collective level,
and we have this problem

00:31:33.780 --> 00:31:36.090 align:middle line:10%
on an individual level.

00:31:36.090 --> 00:31:39.910 align:middle line:10%
It wasn't supposed to be
like this and in fact,

00:31:39.910 --> 00:31:43.890 align:middle line:10%
when we start living according
to the definition of who

00:31:43.890 --> 00:31:47.520 align:middle line:10%
we really are and start
wiping that hard drive

00:31:47.520 --> 00:31:52.887 align:middle line:10%
clean, only then will we evolve
to another level, only then.

00:31:52.887 --> 00:31:55.470 align:middle line:10%
>> REGINA MEREDITH: And you say
it's about the last 250 years,

00:31:55.470 --> 00:31:56.270 align:middle line:10%
right?

00:31:56.270 --> 00:31:58.170 align:middle line:84%
Since this paradigm
has really taken

00:31:58.170 --> 00:32:00.965 align:middle line:84%
hold within our psyche,
maybe even less.

00:32:00.965 --> 00:32:03.090 align:middle line:10%
>> MCTAGGART: Yes I mean,
there's always been cases

00:32:03.090 --> 00:32:06.060 align:middle line:10%
of people wanting to be
aggressive or whatever

00:32:06.060 --> 00:32:09.900 align:middle line:10%
or societies where
people were in charge.

00:32:09.900 --> 00:32:12.870 align:middle line:10%
But prior to Newton,
we had much more

00:32:12.870 --> 00:32:16.920 align:middle line:10%
of a holistic view of ourselves
in relation to the cosmos.

00:32:16.920 --> 00:32:20.040 align:middle line:10%
Newton really essentially
ripped us out of that

00:32:20.040 --> 00:32:24.450 align:middle line:10%
and created a world
of individual things

00:32:24.450 --> 00:32:26.580 align:middle line:10%
and really defined nothingness.

00:32:26.580 --> 00:32:29.700 align:middle line:10%
And so it became a real
understanding of ours

00:32:29.700 --> 00:32:33.180 align:middle line:10%
that we end with the hair
on our skin at which point

00:32:33.180 --> 00:32:35.010 align:middle line:10%
the rest of the universe begins.

00:32:35.010 --> 00:32:38.220 align:middle line:10%
And that, it's
hard to understand

00:32:38.220 --> 00:32:41.550 align:middle line:10%
how much that
definition of ourselves

00:32:41.550 --> 00:32:46.020 align:middle line:10%
really informs how we operate,
because not all cultures.

00:32:46.020 --> 00:32:50.140 align:middle line:10%
Do many Indigenous cultures
think very differently.

00:32:50.140 --> 00:32:53.470 align:middle line:84%
They think of us themselves
as being all connected,

00:32:53.470 --> 00:32:58.140 align:middle line:84%
and from that, they create a
very different kind of society.

00:32:58.140 --> 00:33:00.847 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Why does
intention works on you?

00:33:00.847 --> 00:33:01.930 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: Why does it work?

00:33:01.930 --> 00:33:03.013 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Why does it work?

00:33:03.013 --> 00:33:05.730 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: Well, I think because
we're focusing our energy.

00:33:05.730 --> 00:33:09.540 align:middle line:84%
And I'll give you an example,
if you're watching the news

00:33:09.540 --> 00:33:11.233 align:middle line:84%
and there's something
quite frightening

00:33:11.233 --> 00:33:12.150 align:middle line:90%
that you're watching--

00:33:12.150 --> 00:33:13.692 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: --which is
most of the time.

00:33:13.692 --> 00:33:16.180 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: --most of the
time, for most people,

00:33:16.180 --> 00:33:20.400 align:middle line:84%
their fear comes out from
their body, from their centers

00:33:20.400 --> 00:33:24.030 align:middle line:84%
and connects with the fear
of what they're seeing.

00:33:24.030 --> 00:33:27.150 align:middle line:84%
And this is what's called
the collective karma.

00:33:27.150 --> 00:33:30.880 align:middle line:84%
So we've all just
connected on fear.

00:33:30.880 --> 00:33:33.390 align:middle line:84%
And as we have
seen this past two

00:33:33.390 --> 00:33:38.640 align:middle line:84%
years of the collective
karma and fear and the virus,

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:39.690 align:middle line:90%
it's been rampant.

00:33:39.690 --> 00:33:43.740 align:middle line:84%
And everybody's connected
that fear fiercely

00:33:43.740 --> 00:33:46.650 align:middle line:90%
and been so affected by it.

00:33:46.650 --> 00:33:50.520 align:middle line:84%
I'm seeing clients now
with post-traumatic stress

00:33:50.520 --> 00:33:53.280 align:middle line:84%
and all kinds of
anxiety disorders,

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:55.840 align:middle line:84%
because of what
they've gone through.

00:33:55.840 --> 00:33:59.850 align:middle line:84%
So my feeling about the
meditation peace project

00:33:59.850 --> 00:34:04.290 align:middle line:84%
is if we can connect that
strongly with a feeling, fear,

00:34:04.290 --> 00:34:07.830 align:middle line:84%
we can connect that
strongly with inner peace.

00:34:07.830 --> 00:34:09.840 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Can people take
care of this themselves

00:34:09.840 --> 00:34:13.139 align:middle line:84%
or do they have to go to
someone like Sonja Grace?

00:34:13.139 --> 00:34:18.659 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: Well, I think that if
I were left to my own devices

00:34:18.659 --> 00:34:23.010 align:middle line:84%
to adjust my back and
not go to a chiropractor,

00:34:23.010 --> 00:34:25.290 align:middle line:84%
I might have a bad
back because I need

00:34:25.290 --> 00:34:27.420 align:middle line:90%
