00:34:27.420 --> 00:34:31.889 align:middle line:84%
I need my acupuncturist
to put the needles in me.

00:34:31.889 --> 00:34:33.810 align:middle line:84%
I'm not going to
put them in myself.

00:34:33.810 --> 00:34:35.909 align:middle line:84%
And I certainly need
my brain surgeon

00:34:35.909 --> 00:34:39.900 align:middle line:90%
to do the brain surgery, not me.

00:34:39.900 --> 00:34:43.110 align:middle line:84%
So yes, I think that
my role and what I

00:34:43.110 --> 00:34:48.570 align:middle line:84%
do for society is important,
because our energy body which

00:34:48.570 --> 00:34:52.469 align:middle line:84%
is around us called the
aura is so important George

00:34:52.469 --> 00:34:55.050 align:middle line:84%
to our physical
health, and being

00:34:55.050 --> 00:34:59.010 align:middle line:84%
able to help people understand
their energy, their chakras,

00:34:59.010 --> 00:35:03.240 align:middle line:84%
what's going on with their
inner body, their organs,

00:35:03.240 --> 00:35:06.960 align:middle line:84%
and how everything
functions is important.

00:35:06.960 --> 00:35:11.148 align:middle line:84%
It takes the responsibility
back to people.

00:35:11.148 --> 00:35:12.690 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Sonja what
do you do to keep

00:35:12.690 --> 00:35:16.050 align:middle line:90%
