very happy person.

00:35:25.960 --> 00:35:29.822 align:middle line:84%
I spend time outside, I go
hiking, I walk miles a day.

00:35:29.822 --> 00:35:31.530 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Do you ever
get down, depressed?

00:35:31.530 --> 00:35:33.450 align:middle line:90%
You're a human being.

00:35:33.450 --> 00:35:34.410 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: I do, George.

00:35:34.410 --> 00:35:38.670 align:middle line:84%
