sorrow and pain, of course.

00:35:38.670 --> 00:35:41.430 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: If you
do, are you still

00:35:41.430 --> 00:35:43.710 align:middle line:84%
able to do what you
do with a client?

00:35:43.710 --> 00:35:44.550 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: Yes.

00:35:44.550 --> 00:35:45.925 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Even
though you're down?

00:35:45.925 --> 00:35:49.620 align:middle line:84%
>>GRACE: No, because I know
how to process those feelings,

00:35:49.620 --> 00:35:52.680 align:middle line:84%
I know how to release
them into the Earth,

00:35:52.680 --> 00:35:57.220 align:middle line:84%
and I know that it's
God's will, not mine.

00:35:57.220 --> 00:36:02.040 align:middle line:84%
So I am aligning myself with
creator, with the Earth,

00:36:02.040 --> 00:36:04.950 align:middle line:90%
and I am allowing things to be.

00:36:04.950 --> 00:36:08.340 align:middle line:84%
It's not about being in
control and changing things.

00:36:08.340 --> 00:36:11.940 align:middle line:84%
It's about accepting
who we are and being

00:36:11.940 --> 00:36:15.420 align:middle line:84%
in a place of accepting
what our karma is.

00:36:15.420 --> 00:36:19.290 align:middle line:84%
We all have past lives where
we have had horrific deaths.

00:36:19.290 --> 00:36:21.750 align:middle line:84%
We've died in war
together, we've

00:36:21.750 --> 00:36:23.910 align:middle line:90%
experienced famine and disease.

00:36:23.910 --> 00:36:26.340 align:middle line:84%
It's not it's not that
we've all come here

00:36:26.340 --> 00:36:30.730 align:middle line:84%
with some perfect past that
nothing will ever happen to us.

00:36:30.730 --> 00:36:32.970 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: What would you
