00:36:38.253 --> 00:36:39.420 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: That's pretty good.

00:36:39.420 --> 00:36:40.220 align:middle line:90%
>>GRACE: Yeah.

00:36:40.220 --> 00:36:42.690 align:middle line:84%
